entries.name: acceptedPart3
entries.text: Good luck on finishing Part Three!

children.name: likeYourName
children.response: Thank you. But it's not my real name. I changed it when I was young.

children.name: help2
children.text: ...sorry, Jira. I'm heading on Part 3 of a Five-Part Quest and I'm not sure if I'm heading the right way.
children.response: Ahhh, Part 3 of 5. It's a good one. Yes, you are heading the right way. Continue on this path to my right and find your way to the East Desert.

children.name: thanks
children.response: You are welcome. And may the Great Ones guide you!
